    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/996d528d05918a88007c4e9f3c627cb4.avif?t=1768818345\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>PLAY WITH STICKERS</i></strong> and feel nostalgic in Sticker Delight - a short, cozy sticker game. Designed for a brief yet memorable playtime of around 30 minutes, the game is suitable for a quick cozy gaming session. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/706ecb3f33d16ef852801596164478b9.poster.avif?t=1768818345\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/706ecb3f33d16ef852801596164478b9.webm?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/706ecb3f33d16ef852801596164478b9.mp4?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Play with Stickers</strong>: Use stickers in the game to progress - drag, drop, or group them. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Witty and Relaxing Puzzles</strong>: Solve a variety of witty and relaxing puzzles made of stickers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intuitive User Experience (UX): </strong>No hand-holding tutorials needed, just dive in and play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short, Sweet, and Non-Grindy</strong>: With a playtime of around 30 minutes, Sticker Delight is perfect for a quick, cozy gaming session. <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/e40554b5e66948239ce50c10e2b0bbb6.poster.avif?t=1768818345\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/e40554b5e66948239ce50c10e2b0bbb6.webm?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/e40554b5e66948239ce50c10e2b0bbb6.mp4?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cozy Atmosphere</strong>: Slow down and immerse yourself in a warm, cozy environment, enhanced by a suitable audio experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize the Dinner</strong>: Name your guests and choose from a selection of delicious Southeast Asian dishes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Your Own Sticker Book</strong>: Collect sticker packs and express yourself using the sticker book. Come back anytime you'd like.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Nostalgic and Heartwarming Experience</strong>: Enjoy nostalgic and heartwarming moments as you step into the shoes of Mia, an adventurous child with a big heart.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/616bd08bd91c92fa726e76c190436b03.poster.avif?t=1768818345\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/616bd08bd91c92fa726e76c190436b03.webm?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053210/extras/616bd08bd91c92fa726e76c190436b03.mp4?t=1768818345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
